reviewText: I saw this on HBO.  It follows the standard format: little bit of story, sex scene, more story, more sex, etc.  Spoiler Alert:  The most of the sex scenes end with the girl killing her partner. Not my cup of tea...
Not the best story, not the worst nudity. Probably just exactly what one is looking for in a soft core.
I bought this movie expecting to see Erika Jordan, but she was only in the first scene. So I am disappointed with this purchase.
Enjoyable, but try Vixens from Venus or Paranormal Sexperiments both were more entertaining if you are a fan of Erika Jordan
